last_episode_to_air.overview: Mera Dil, Mera Dushman is a Pakistani television series premiered on 3 February 2020 on ARY Digital. It is directed by Syed Ali Raza Usama and co-produced by Humayun Saeed and Samina Humayun Saeed under Six Sigma Plus and Next Level Entertainment.
